@{b}CONTENTS@{ub}

    This program shows an URL in your web browser. Example usage:

    showurl URL="http://golded.tripod.com"

@{b}INSTALLATION@{ub}

    Doubleclick the setup icon or manually place the showurl program  in  the
    path,  e.g.  in  the "c:" folder. This program needs the "remote.library"
    from the RA Remote Access package which can be found  on  Aminet  servers
    (util/libs/ra.lha).
@endnode
